{
  "stem": "22586.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I had to take an exam to get into the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to gymnasium for eight years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But actually, I went to the public school, the Czech gymnasium for four years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the Hungarians occupied us and we couldn't go to the public school, so I transferred to the Hebrew gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1938, we still had radios and newspapers that we could get.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew-- we were very well aware that war has broken out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only later that we could not have any radios, couldn't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] couldn't find out what's going on and later on, because newspapers were not-- I'm sure not reporting what was going on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a few people who had radios clandestinely, I mean secretly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I know that my father had a friend who had a shortwave radio.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he used to go to his house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would listen to radio and come home and tell us what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But other than that, you could not openly own radios then, Jewish people couldn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and that's when anti-Semitism has begun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one time-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] excuse me-- [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On Fridays, my father used to go down to the river, where the fisherman were, and buy fresh fish for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, he went down to the river, and he saw one of the fishermen beating a young boy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father said, why are you beating him?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the fisherman got very-- and he said, well, you just stop it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my-- the fisherman got into an argument with Father, my father that it is none of his business.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
